<L>__{exterior washington day}
<A>__{the city is a swarm of people. at the moment the populace is displaying both sorrow and anticipation. sorrow for the loss of the president. many are dressed in black, and black crepe hangs nearly everywhere. black armbands are frequently seen, and the occasional american flag hung at half mast. as well, there are portraits of harrison at varying locations. having arrived in washington, solomon, hamilton and brown}
<B>__{ride onward in their carriage.}
